## ModelFetcherConfig interface

Represents an extended model configuration for a given model for fetchable models

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export interface ModelFetcherConfig<TState = UnknownState, TModel extends StateModels<TState> = StateModels<TState>> extends ModelConfig<TState, TModel> 
```
<b>Extends:</b> ModelConfig&lt;TState, TModel&gt;

## Properties

|  Property | Type | Description |
|  --- | --- | --- |
|  [fetchUrl?](./model-state-fetcher.modelfetcherconfig.fetchurl.md) | string | <i>(Optional)</i> Url endpoint that serves the model data when fetched. If not set, fetching will be disabled for given model. |
